title: 11600 Bar Keepers Liquid Cleanser and Polisher Liquid 13oz.
description:
BAR KEEPERS FRIEND LIQUID 13 OZ 

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Kitchen:

● Sinks - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean sinks made of porcelain, stainless steel or solid surfaces. Other cleansers containing bleach are not recommended for stainless steel. BKFr is also recommended for sinks in bronze, brass and copper. 
● Faucets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean faucets in chrome, brass and other finishes. 
● Countertops - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean countertops made of laminate, composite and solid surfaces. 
● Cooktops - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean and remove discoloration on glass and ceramic cooktops. 
● Cookware - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean and shine pots and pans made of stainless steel and copper. 
Appliances - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean stainless steel kitchen appliances. 
● Tile & Grout - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean porcelain and ceramic tile. Bar Keepers Friend also cleans light colored grout 

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Bathroom:

● Sinks - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean sinks made of porcelain, ceramic or solid surfaces. 
● Bathtubs - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean bathtubs made of porcelain, ceramic, acrylic or fiberglass. 
● Faucets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean faucets in chrome, brass and other finishes. 
● Showers - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean showers made of porcelain tile, ceramic tile, acrylic or fiberglass. Bar Keepers Friend also cleans glass shower doors. 
● Toilets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean toilets without harsh chemicals. 

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Garage:

● Car Care - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean wheels, chrome, glass and more. 
● Bicycles - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean rust from bicycles. 
● Golf Clubs - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean stainless steel and composite golf clubs. 
● Tools & More - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean garden tools, grills, wood deck stains, rust on stone and masonry and even the cymbals for a garage band drummer!

• Controls gas valve, ignitor, blower motor, inducer, humidifier and air cleaner

• Secondary brownout voltage protection 
• Diagnostic fault codes (blinking LED) for simple troubleshooting

title: BFK21 Bar Keepers Friend All Purpose Cleaning Powder, 21oz.
description:
BAR KEEPERS FRIEND 21 OUNCE BKF21

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Kitchen:

● Sinks - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean sinks made of porcelain, stainless steel or solid surfaces. Other cleansers containing bleach are not recommended for stainless steel. BKFr is also recommended for sinks in bronze, brass and copper. 
● Faucets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean faucets in chrome, brass and other finishes. 
● Countertops - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean countertops made of laminate, composite and solid surfaces. 
● Cooktops - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean and remove discoloration on glass and ceramic cooktops. 
● Cookware - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean and shine pots and pans made of stainless steel and copper. 
Appliances - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean stainless steel kitchen appliances. 
● Tile & Grout - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean porcelain and ceramic tile. Bar Keepers Friend also cleans light colored grout 

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Bathroom:

● Sinks - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean sinks made of porcelain, ceramic or solid surfaces. 
● Bathtubs - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean bathtubs made of porcelain, ceramic, acrylic or fiberglass. 
● Faucets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean faucets in chrome, brass and other finishes. 
● Showers - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean showers made of porcelain tile, ceramic tile, acrylic or fiberglass. Bar Keepers Friend also cleans glass shower doors. 
● Toilets - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean toilets without harsh chemicals. 

Use Bar Keepers Friend in the Garage:

● Car Care - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean wheels, chrome, glass and more. 
● Bicycles - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean rust from bicycles. 
● Golf Clubs - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean stainless steel and composite golf clubs. 
● Tools & More - Use Bar Keepers Friend to clean garden tools, grills, wood deck stains, rust on stone and masonry and even the cymbals for a garage band drummer!
